| Netflix | Watch unlimited TV shows and movies | Limited new content            | Stream endless entertainment. New hits added weekly.             |
| Amazon  | Shop anything, delivered fast       | Concerns about product quality | Shop millions of verified products. Fast delivery, easy returns. |

### 3. Subheading

**Key components:**

- Expand on your header
- Explain how your product works
- Support your bold claims
- Keep it brief (1-2 sentences)

**Examples from top companies:**

| Company | Header                              | Subheader                                                                                                |
| ------- | ----------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
